  - 10/10 step law_enforced kiem[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME]
  - cell boot-dovan den[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] treng[C5:RN_ANG_ENG] thai[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] tho
  - 4 LAW khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] vi pham[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]
  - 8 step Signal Lifecycle day[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] du[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME]

$boot_fail_condition:
  - Teng[C2:RN_ANG_ENG] 0 SURVIVAL khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] ready → abort pre-boot
  - Step DISSIPATE → abort
  - Step OSCILLATE qua[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] nguong[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] → abort
  - Vi pham[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] bat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] ky[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] LAW → abort
  - Cell khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] den[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] tho → fail

